{{Infobox Union |name= Finansförbundet |country= [[Sweden]] |affiliation= [[Swedish Confederation of Professional Employees|TCO]] |members= 33,000 |full_name= Financial Sector Union of Sweden |native_name= |image= [[Image:Finansforbundet logo.png|200px]] |founded= |current= |head= |dissolved_date= |dissolved_state= |merged_into= |office= [[Stockholm]], Sweden |people= |website= [http://www.finansforbundet.se www.finansforbundet.se] |footnotes= }} <!-- Include all unused fields for future use. See [[template talk:Infobox Union]] for usage. -->
The '''Financial Sector Union of Sweden''' ({{lang-sv|'''Finansförbundet'''}}) is a [[trade union]] in Sweden.
Finansförbundet has a membership of 33,000 and represents workers in: * Banks * Financial institutions * [[Credit broker]]s * Mortgage companies * Stock brokers * Other companies in the financial sector
Finansförbundet is affiliated with the [[Swedish Confederation of Professional Employees]].
==External links== *{{official website|http://www.finansforbundet.se}}
