'''Tatabrada TV''' is a [[Bosnia]]n local commercial [[Cable television]] channel based in [[Srebrenik]], [[Bosnia and Herzegovina|BiH]]<ref name="Korisnici Dozvole za televizijsko emitovanje putem drugih mreža">{{cite web |author1=www.rak.ba |title=Korisnici Dozvole za televizijsko emitovanje putem drugih mreža |url=https://rak.ba/bos/index.php?uid=1273787112 |website=www.rak.ba |publisher=www.rak.ba |accessdate=10 November 2018 |language=Bosnian |date=19 October 2018}}</ref>. The program is produced in [[Bosnian language]], and it is available via [[Cable television|cable systems]] throughout the [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]].
